OL,6,FA mother says she has been forced to
OL,7,Fconsider buying a disused church for
OL,8,Fher disabled three-year-old son
OL,9,Fbecause grant funding will not cover
OL,10,Fadaptations to their home.
OL,12,FRachel Devereux, who lives in , says
OL,13,Ffundraising for the church is the
OL,14,Ffamily's only option as the grant
OL,15,Favailable from the local authority to
OL,16,Fmodify homes has not increased in 16
OL,17,Fyears.
