OL,4,Cson due to lack of suitable homes
OL,6,F"We have seen a local church for sale,
OL,7,Fwhich we are now considering buying.
OL,8,FIt would be flat and more suitable for
OL,9,FHero."
OL,11,FRachel said Hero's diagnosis came as a
OL,12,F"massive blow".
OL,14,F"Your life plans and your imagination
OL,15,Fof what life will be like changes in
OL,16,Fan instant," she said.
OL,18,F"(But) instead of seeing it as a death
OL,19,Fsentence, we are seeing it as a life
OL,20,Fsentence, and we want to give him the
OL,21,Fbest life he possibly can have."
