OL,4,Cson due to lack of suitable homes
OL,6,FRachel, who has three other children,
OL,7,Fsaid the council had advised the
OL,8,Ffamily to move or accept a council
OL,9,Fhouse, but local four-bedroom homes
OL,10,Fwere too small for wheelchair and
OL,11,Fhoist access.
OL,13,FShe wants to see more wheelchair-
OL,14,Ffriendly housing built, but in the
OL,15,Fmeantime has started an to raise
OL,16,Fawareness and funds for Hero's future.
OL,18,FShe runs a support group for other
OL,19,Fparents and hopes to be able to run
OL,20,Fsessions at the church if the bid is
OL,21,Fsuccessful.
