OL,6,F"I see the mortgage as our
OL,7,Fresponsibility, but we would like to
OL,8,Ffundraise for the adaptations because
OL,9,Fit is also going to help the
OL,10,Fcommunity," she said.
OL,12,FGrants for home adaptations are handed
OL,13,Fout by the local authority, but are
OL,14,Ffunded by the government.
OL,16,FKirklees Council said it was aware the
OL,17,Fmaximum grant had not changed since
OL,18,F2008.
